Main use cases: {{mainUseCases}}
Differentiation: {{differentiation}}
Proof points: {{proofPoints}}
Availability: {{availability}}
Product status: {{productStatus}}
Competitor context: {{competitorContext}}

Maker names and team context: {{makerNames}}
Maker story: {{makerStory}}
Build journey: {{buildJourney}}
