Build one complete sales proposal for {{providerName}} to present to {{clientName}}. The proposed offer is {{offerName}}. Use the supplied facts to explain the client’s situation, define the proposed solution, describe the work and commercial terms, reduce decision friction, and lead naturally to the requested next step.

